BENUTZERANFRAGE:
Erstelle mir ein Modal mit einem Formular für eine Adresseingabe. Es soll einen Öffnen-Button, Titel, Inputfelder für Straße, PLZ und Stadt haben, und einen Speichern-Button. Nutze Tailwind CSS.

title:
Modal Formular für Adresseingabe

Öffnen-Button:
<button class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700">Adresse einfügen</button>

Modal:
<div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black opacity-50 flex justify-center items-center hidden" id="addressModal">
  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-md">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Adresse eingeben</h2>
    <form>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="street" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-1">Straße:</label>
        <input type="text" id="street" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="postalCode" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-1">PLZ:</label>
        <input type="text" id="postalCode" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="city" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-1">Stadt:</label>
        <input type="text" id="city" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="text-white bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-green-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 dark:bg-green-600 dark:hover:bg-green-700">Speichern</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

JavaScript (für Öffnen-Schließen des Modals):
document.getElementById('addressModal').addEventListener('click', function(event) {
  if (event.target.classList.contains('fixed')) {
    this.classList.add('hidden');
  }
});

document.querySelector('.text-blue-700').addEventListener('click', function() {
  document.getElementById('addressModal').classList.remove('hidden');
});
